The '''Malreaux rose''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of flower that was developed by the [[House Malreaux|Malreaux family]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vjun/Legends|Vjun]]. They were said to be such a deep red, that they appeared black or violet.

